Package org.sparadrap.model.MedicineModel

Class Medicine

java.lang.Object
org.sparadrap.model.MedicineModel.Medicine
public class Medicine extends Object
Represents a Medicine entity in the system. Contains details such as name, category, price, start date, quantity, and prescription requirement.
